                    <li class="cs-paper-item">
                        <a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar?q=Simulating+Blood+Flow+Left+Atrium+Multiscale+Electromechanics+Shi" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="cs-paper-link">
                            Simulating Blood Flow in Left Atrium using a Personalized Multiscale Electromechanics Modeling Framework (2024, APS)
