                        </a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="cs-paper-item">
                        <a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar?q=Optimization+Framework+Personalize+Passive+Cardiac+Mechanics+Shi" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="cs-paper-link">
