                        <a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar?q=Modular+Framework+Implicit+3D+0D+Coupling+Cardiac+Mechanics" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="cs-paper-link">
                            A Modular Framework for Implicit 3D–0D Coupling in Cardiac Mechanics (2024, CMAME)
                            <span class="cs-link-icon">↗</span>
                        </a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="cs-paper-item">
                        <a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar?q=Software+Benchmark+Cardiac+Elastodynamics" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="cs-paper-link">
